org.jorlib.frameworks.columnGeneration.branchAndPrice.branchingDecisions

Interface BranchingDecisionListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMaster, AbstractPricingProblem, AbstractPricingProblemSolver

    public interface BranchingDecisionListener
    Interface defining a BranchingDecision Listener. Every BranchingDecision listener is informed about branching decisions which are executed.

    Author:
    Joris Kinable
